<h1>The Ranger Broadcasting System </h1>
<p>
  <i>&ldquo;We interrupt our regularly scheduled program to bring you this important message . . . &rdquo;</i>
</p>

<div class="d-lg-flex justify-content-between">
  <section class="me-lg-4">
    <h3>On Playa Broadcast Actions</h3>
    <div class="border rounded p-2 mb-2 text-center">
      <LinkTo @route="admin.rbs.broadcast" @query={{hash type="recruit-position"}}
              class="btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block">
        Message off-duty SPECIAL TEAM RANGERS
      </LinkTo>
      A team (e.g., Green Dots, LEALs, Shift Leads) in the city is understaffed
      Call up the willing specialized ranks.<br> Sent via text message and email only, NO CLUBHOUSE MESSAGES.
    </div>
    {{#if (has-role "megaphone")}}
      <div class="border rounded p-2 mb-2 text-center">
        <LinkTo @route="admin.rbs.broadcast"
                @query={{hash type="recruit-dirt"}}
                class="btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block">
          Message off-duty DIRT RANGERS
        </LinkTo>
        City currently is understaffed. Call upon willing off-duty Dirt Rangers to help out. Sent via text message and
        email.
      </div>
      <div class="border rounded p-2 mb-2 text-center">
        <LinkTo @route="admin.rbs.broadcast" @query={{hash type="onshift"}} class="btn btn-warning btn-lg btn-block">
          Text all ON-SHIFT RANGERS
        </LinkTo>
        Radio repeater failure, imminent city split, etc. Text message only.
      </div>
    {{/if}}
    {{#if (has-role "megaphone-emergency-onplaya")}}
      <div class="border rounded p-2 mb-2 text-center">
        <LinkTo @route="admin.rbs.broadcast" @query={{hash type="emergency"}} class="btn btn-danger btn-lg btn-block">
          Emergency Broadcast to ALL ON-PLAYA RANGERS
        </LinkTo>
        <div class="text-danger">
          {{fa-icon "bell"}} <b>The Big Red Button</b> {{fa-icon "bell"}}<br>
        </div>
        All hands on deck. Fatality, fire, plane crash, or other crises has happend.
      </div>
    {{/if}}
  </section>
  <section>
    <h3>General Broadcast Actions</h3>
    <div class="border rounded p-2 mb-2 text-center">
      <LinkTo @route="admin.rbs.broadcast" @query={{hash type="slot"}} class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg btn-block">SHIFT
        SIGN-UP BROADCAST
      </LinkTo>
      Notify Rangers signed up for a particular shift of a time change, or other related information. Text, email,
      and/or Clubhouse message.
    </div>
    <div class="border rounded p-2 mb-2 text-center">
      <LinkTo @route="admin.rbs.broadcast" @query={{hash type="position"}} class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg btn-block">
        TEAM/POSITION BROADCAST
      </LinkTo>
      Send a message to everyone who holds a position or is on a Special Team. Useful for meeting requests. Text,
      email, and/or Clubhouse message.
    </div>
    {{#if (has-role "admin" "megaphone")}}
      <div class="border rounded p-2 mb-2 text-center">
        <LinkTo @route="admin.rbs.broadcast" @query={{hash type="general"}} class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg btn-block">
          GENERAL BROADCAST
        </LinkTo>
        General broadcast to most Clubhouse users. Text, email, and/or Clubhouse message.
      </div>
    {{/if}}
  </section>
</div>
{{#if (has-role "tech-ninja")}}
  <UiSection>
    <:title>Administration</:title>
    <:body>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <LinkTo @route="admin.rbs.broadcast-log">View broadcast log</LinkTo>
        </li>
        <li>
          <LinkTo @route="admin.rbs.broadcast-log" @query={{hash failed=true}}>View failed broadcasts</LinkTo>
        </li>
        <li>
          <LinkTo @route="admin.rbs.message-log">View message log</LinkTo>
        </li>
        <li>
          <LinkTo @route="admin.rbs.unknown-phones">View unknown phone log</LinkTo>
        </li>
        <li>
          <LinkTo @route="admin.rbs.stats">Phone number stats</LinkTo>
        </li>
        <li>
          <LinkTo @route="admin.rbs.unverified-stopped">View unverified &amp; stopped numbers</LinkTo>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </:body>
  </UiSection>
{{/if}}
